#: TWLight/applications/views.py:858
#, python-brace-format
msgid "This application cannot be modified since this partner is now part of our <a href='{bundle}'>bundle access</a>. If you are eligible, you can access this resource from <a href='{library}'>your library</a>. <a href='{contact}'>Contact us</a> if you have any questions."
msgstr "Ní féidir an t-iarratas seo a mhodhnú ós rud é go bhfuil an comhpháirtí seo mar chuid dár <a href='{bundle}'>rochtain phacáiste</a> anois. Má tá tú incháilithe, is féidir leat rochtain a fháil ar an acmhainn seo ó <a href='{library}'>do leabharlann</a>. <a href='{contact}'>Déan teagmháil linn</a> má tá aon cheist agat."

