#. Translators: This email is sent to users when we invite them to respond to a survey. Don't translate Jinja variables in curly braces like link. Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named (click through from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library).
#: TWLight/emails/templates/emails/survey_active_user-body-html.html:5
#, python-format
msgid "<p>Hi,</p> <p>We are currently running a survey to understand how editors use The Wikipedia Library. According to our records, you have logged in to The Wikipedia Library at least once, so we would love to hear from you!</p> <p><a href=\"%(link)s\">%(link)s</a></p> <p>We really appreciate your feedback - this survey will help us understand how The Wikipedia Library is currently being used, and where it could use improvement. Your responses will directly impact how the Wikimedia Foundation prioritises technical and partnership work for this project.</p> <p>The survey should take 5-10 minutes to complete.</p> <p>If you would like to opt-out of being contacted with future Wikipedia Library surveys, please let us know by emailing wikipedialibrary@wikimedia.org and we will remove you from any future mailing.</p> <p>Thanks,</p> <p>The Wikipedia Library team</p>"
msgstr "<p>Haigh,</p> <p>Táimid ag reáchtáil suirbhé faoi láthair chun tuiscint a fháil ar an gcaoi a n-úsáideann eagarthóirí Leabharlann Vicipéid. De réir ár dtaifead, tá tú logáilte isteach i Leabharlann Vicipéid uair amháin ar a laghad, mar sin ba bhreá linn cloisteáil uait!</p> <p><a href=\"%(link)s\">%(link)s</a></p> <p>Táimid fíorbhuíoch as d'aiseolas - cabhróidh an suirbhé seo linn tuiscint a fháil ar an gcaoi a bhfuil Leabharlann Vicipéid á húsáid faoi láthair, agus cá bhféadfaí feabhas a chur uirthi. Beidh tionchar díreach ag do chuid freagraí ar an gcaoi a dtugann Fondúireacht Wikimedia tosaíocht d'obair theicniúil agus chomhpháirtíochta don tionscadal seo.</p> <p>Ba chóir go dtógfadh an suirbhé 5-10 nóiméad le críochnú.</p> <p>Más mian leat diúltú do theagmháil a dhéanamh le suirbhéanna Leabharlann Vicipéid amach anseo, cuir in iúl dúinn trí ríomhphost a sheoladh chuig wikipedialibrary@wikimedia.org agus bainfimid thú as aon phost amach anseo.</p> <p>Go raibh maith agat,</p> <p>Foireann Leabharlann Vicipéid</p>"

#. Translators: This email is sent to users when we invite them to respond to a survey. Don't translate Jinja variables in curly braces like link. Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named (click through from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library).
#: TWLight/emails/templates/emails/survey_active_user-body-text.html:3
#, python-format
msgid "Hi, We are currently running a survey to understand how editors use The Wikipedia Library. According to our records, you have logged in to The Wikipedia Library at least once, so we would love to hear from you! %(link)s We really appreciate your feedback - this survey will help us understand how The Wikipedia Library is currently being used, and where it could use improvement. Your responses will directly impact how the Wikimedia Foundation prioritises technical and partnership work for this project. The survey should take 5-10 minutes to complete. If you would like to opt-out of being contacted with future Wikipedia Library surveys, please let us know by emailing wikipedialibrary@wikimedia.org and we will remove you from any future mailing. Thanks, The Wikipedia Library team"
msgstr "Haigh, Táimid ag déanamh suirbhé faoi láthair chun tuiscint a fháil ar an gcaoi a n-úsáideann eagarthóirí Leabharlann Vicipéid. De réir ár dtaifead, tá tú logáilte isteach i Leabharlann Vicipéid uair amháin ar a laghad, mar sin ba bhreá linn cloisteáil uait! %(link)s Cuirimid fíorluach ar d'aiseolas - cabhróidh an suirbhé seo linn tuiscint a fháil ar an gcaoi a bhfuil Leabharlann Vicipéid á húsáid faoi láthair, agus cá bhféadfaí feabhas a chur uirthi. Beidh tionchar díreach ag do chuid freagraí ar an gcaoi a dtugann Fondúireacht Wikimedia tús áite d'obair theicniúil agus chomhpháirtíochta don tionscadal seo. Ba chóir go dtógfadh an suirbhé 5-10 nóiméad le cur i gcrích. Más mian leat diúltú do theagmháil a dhéanamh leat maidir le suirbhéanna Leabharlann Vicipéid amach anseo, cuir in iúl dúinn trí ríomhphost a sheoladh chuig wikipedialibrary@wikimedia.org agus bainfimid thú as aon phost amach anseo. Go raibh maith agat, Foireann Leabharlann Vicipéid"

#. Translators: This is the subject of an email sent to users when we invite them to respond to a survey. Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named (click through from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library).
#. Translators: email subject line
#: TWLight/emails/templates/emails/survey_active_user-subject.html:4
#: TWLight/users/management/commands/survey_active_users.py:118
msgid "The Wikipedia Library needs your help!"
msgstr "Tá do chabhair ag teastáil ó Leabharlann Vicipéid!"

#. Translators: This email is sent to users when they have an account that is soon to expire. Don't translate Jinja variables in curly braces like partner_name or partner_link; don't translate html tags either. Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named (click through from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library).
#: TWLight/emails/templates/emails/user_renewal_notice-body-html.html:5
#, python-format
msgid "<p>Dear %(user)s,</p> <p>According to our records, your access to %(partner_name)s will soon expire and you may lose access. If you want to continue making use of your free account, you can request renewal of your account by clicking the 'Renew' or 'Extend' button at %(partner_link)s.</p> <p>Best,</p> <p>The Wikipedia Library</p> <p>You can disable these emails in your user page preferences: https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/users/</p>"
msgstr "<p>A %(user)s a chara,</p> <p>De réir ár dtaifead, rachaidh do rochtain ar %(partner_name)s in éag go luath agus d'fhéadfá rochtain a chailleadh. Más mian leat leanúint ar aghaidh ag baint úsáide as do chuntas saor in aisce, is féidir leat athnuachan do chuntais a iarraidh trí chliceáil ar an gcnaipe 'Athnuaigh' nó 'Síneadh' ag %(partner_link)s.</p> <p>Is fearr,</p> <p>Leabharlann Vicipéide</p> <p>Is féidir leat na ríomhphoist seo a dhíchumasú i do chuid roghanna leathanaigh úsáideora: https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/users/</p>"

