#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/). Wikimedia Foundation should not be translated.
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:29
msgid "All users receive immediate access to some collections, which can be browsed by clicking the 'Access collection' buttons or using the search bar at the top of the page. Other collections require an application before access is granted, and may be accessed directly or via an individual login or access code. Volunteer coordinators, who have signed non-disclosure agreements with the Wikimedia Foundation, review these applications and work with publishers to get you your free access."
msgstr "Faigheann gach úsáideoir rochtain láithreach ar roinnt bailiúcháin, agus is féidir iad a bhrabhsáil trí chliceáil ar na cnaipí 'Rochtain ar bhailiúchán' nó trí úsáid a bhaint as an mbarra cuardaigh ag barr an leathanaigh. Éilíonn bailiúcháin eile iarratas sula ndeonaítear rochtain, agus is féidir rochtain a fháil orthu go díreach nó trí logáil isteach aonair nó cód rochtana. Déanann comhordaitheoirí deonacha, a bhfuil comhaontuithe neamhnochta sínithe acu le Fondúireacht Wikimedia, athbhreithniú ar na hiarratais seo agus oibríonn siad le foilsitheoirí chun rochtain saor in aisce a fháil duit."

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/). Don't translate terms_url.
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:43
#, python-format
msgid "For more information about how your information is stored and reviewed please see our <a class=\"twl-links\" href=\"%(terms_url)s\"> terms of use and privacy policy</a>. Accounts you apply for are also subject to the Terms of Use provided by each partner’s platform; please review them."
msgstr "Chun tuilleadh eolais a fháil faoin gcaoi a stóráiltear agus a ndéantar athbhreithniú ar d’fhaisnéis, féach ar ár <a class=\"twl-links\" href=\"%(terms_url)s\">téarmaí úsáide agus ár mbeartas príobháideachta</a>. Tá cuntais a ndéanann tú iarratas orthu faoi réir na dTéarmaí Úsáide a sholáthraíonn ardán gach comhpháirtí freisin; déan athbhreithniú orthu le do thoil."

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:51
msgid "Who can receive access?"
msgstr "Cé a fhéadfaidh rochtain a fháil?"

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/). Wikimedia Foundation should not be translated.
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:55
msgid "Any active editor in good standing can receive access. For publishers with limited numbers of accounts, applications are reviewed based on the editor’s needs and contributions. If you think you could use access to one of our partner resources and are an active editor in any project supported by the Wikimedia Foundation, please apply."
msgstr "Is féidir le haon eagarthóir gníomhach i riocht maith rochtain a fháil. I gcás foilsitheoirí a bhfuil líon teoranta cuntas acu, déantar athbhreithniú ar iarratais bunaithe ar riachtanais agus ranníocaíochtaí an eagarthóra. Má cheapann tú go bhféadfá rochtain ar cheann dár n-acmhainní comhpháirtíochta a úsáid agus má tá tú i d’eagarthóir gníomhach in aon tionscadal a fhaigheann tacaíocht ó Fhondúireacht Wikimedia, déan iarratas le do thoil."

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:65
msgid "Any editor can use the library if they meet a few basic requirements:"
msgstr "Is féidir le haon eagarthóir an leabharlann a úsáid má chomhlíonann siad cúpla bunriachtanas:"

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:71
msgid "You have an account that is a minimum of 6 months old"
msgstr "Tá cuntas agat atá sé mhí d'aois ar a laghad"

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:75
msgid "You have made a minimum of 500 edits to Wikimedia projects"
msgstr "Tá 500 eagarthóireacht ar a laghad déanta agat ar thionscadail Wikimedia."

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:79
msgid "You have made at least 10 edits to Wikimedia projects in the last month"
msgstr "Tá 10 eagarthóireacht ar a laghad déanta agat ar thionscadail Wikimedia le mí anuas."

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:83
msgid "You are not currently blocked from editing a Wikimedia project"
msgstr "Níl bac ort faoi láthair tionscadal Wikimedia a chur in eagar"

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/)
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:89
msgid "If you are applying for an available collection, please first check that you don't already have access through another library or institution. If you do, please consider using that access rather than taking up a seat for this resource in The Wikipedia Library."
msgstr "Más rud é go bhfuil tú ag cur isteach ar bhailiúchán atá ar fáil, déan cinnte ar dtús nach bhfuil rochtain agat air cheana féin trí leabharlann nó institiúid eile. Má tá, smaoinigh ar an rochtain sin a úsáid seachas suíochán a ghlacadh don acmhainn seo i Leabharlann Vicipéid."

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/)
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:99
msgid "If your account is blocked on one or more Wikimedia projects, you may still be granted access to The Wikipedia Library. You will need to contact the Wikipedia Library team, who will review your blocks. If you have been blocked for content issues, most notably copyright violations, or have multiple long-term blocks, we may decline your request. Additionally, if your block status changes after being approved, you will need to request another review."
msgstr "Má tá do chuntas blocáilte ar thionscadal amháin nó níos mó de chuid Wikimedia, féadfar rochtain a thabhairt duit fós ar Leabharlann Vicipéid. Beidh ort teagmháil a dhéanamh le foireann Leabharlann Vicipéid, a dhéanfaidh athbhreithniú ar do bhloic. Má cuireadh bac ort mar gheall ar shaincheisteanna ábhair, go háirithe sáruithe cóipchirt, nó má tá roinnt blocálacha fadtéarmacha agat, féadfaimid d’iarratas a dhiúltú. Ina theannta sin, má athraíonn stádas do bhloic tar éis duit a bheith ceadaithe, beidh ort athbhreithniú eile a iarraidh."

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:110
msgid "What do I do after I get access?"
msgstr "Cad a dhéanfaidh mé tar éis dom rochtain a fháil?"

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:114
msgid "Approved editors <i>may</i> use their access to:"
msgstr "<i>Féadfaidh</i> eagarthóirí ceadaithe a rochtain a úsáid ar:"

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:118
msgid "Search, view, retrieve, and display partner content"
msgstr "Cuardaigh, féach, aisghabh agus taispeáin ábhar comhpháirtíochta"

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:122
msgid "Electronically save partner content"
msgstr "Ábhar comhpháirtíochta a shábháil go leictreonach"

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:126
msgid "Print out single copies of partner content"
msgstr "Priontáil cóipeanna aonair d'ábhar comhpháirtíochta"

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:132
msgid "Approved editors <i>should not</i>:"
msgstr "<i>Níor cheart</i> d'eagarthóirí ceadaithe:"

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:136
msgid "Share their account logins or passwords with others, or sell their access to other parties"
msgstr "A logáil isteach nó a bpasfhocail chuntais a roinnt le daoine eile, nó a rochtain a dhíol le páirtithe eile"

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:140
msgid "Mass scrape or mass download partner content"
msgstr "Ábhar comhpháirtíochta a scríobadh go mais nó a íoslódáil go mais"

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:144
msgid "Systematically make printed or electronic copies of multiple extracts of restricted content available for any purpose"
msgstr "Cóipeanna clóite nó leictreonacha de shleachta iolracha d’ábhar srianta a chur ar fáil go córasach chun aon chríche"

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/). Stub is a technical term for a short Wikipedia article, use the appropriate Wikipedia term in your language.
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:148
msgid "Datamine metadata without permission, in order, for instance, to use metadata for auto-created stub articles"
msgstr "Meiteashonraí a mhianadóireacht gan chead, d’fhonn, mar shampla, meiteashonraí a úsáid le haghaidh ailt stumpa a cruthaíodh go huathoibríoch"

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:154
msgid "Respecting these agreements allows us to continue growing the partnerships available to the community."
msgstr "Trí na comhaontuithe seo a urramú, is féidir linn leanúint de bheith ag fás na gcomhpháirtíochtaí atá ar fáil don phobal."

#. Translators: This is the heading for a section on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:160
msgid "EZProxy"
msgstr "EZProxy"

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:164
msgid "EZProxy is a proxy server used to authenticate users for many Wikipedia Library partners. Users sign into EZProxy via the Library Card platform to verify that they are authorized users, and then the server accesses requested resources using its own IP address."
msgstr "Is freastalaí seachfhreastalaí é EZProxy a úsáidtear chun úsáideoirí a fhíordheimhniú do go leor comhpháirtithe Leabharlann Vicipéid. Síníonn úsáideoirí isteach in EZProxy tríd an ardán Cárta Leabharlainne chun a fhíorú gur úsáideoirí údaraithe iad, agus ansin rochtainíonn an freastalaí acmhainní iarrtha ag baint úsáide as a sheoladh IP féin."

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:173
msgid "You may notice that when accessing resources via EZProxy that URLs are dynamically rewritten. This is why we recommend logging in via the Library Card platform rather than going directly to the unproxied partner website. When in doubt, check the URL for ‘idm.oclc’. If it’s there, then you’re connected via EZProxy."
msgstr "B’fhéidir go dtabharfaidh tú faoi deara go ndéantar URLanna a athscríobh go dinimiciúil agus tú ag rochtain acmhainní trí EZProxy. Sin é an fáth a mholaimid logáil isteach tríd an ardán Cárta Leabharlainne seachas dul go díreach chuig suíomh Gréasáin an chomhpháirtí neamh-phróiseáilte. Má tá amhras ort, seiceáil an URL le haghaidh ‘idm.oclc’. Má tá sé ann, ansin tá tú ceangailte trí EZProxy."

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:182
msgid "Typically once you’ve logged in your session will remain active in your browser for up to two hours after you’ve finished searching. Note that use of EZProxy requires you to enable cookies. If you are having problems you should also try clearing your cache and restarting your browser."
msgstr "De ghnáth, nuair a bheidh tú logáilte isteach, fanfaidh do sheisiún gníomhach i do bhrabhsálaí ar feadh suas le dhá uair an chloig tar éis duit an cuardach a chríochnú. Tabhair faoi deara go n-éilíonn úsáid EZProxy ort fianáin a chumasú. Má bhíonn fadhbanna agat, ba cheart duit iarracht a dhéanamh do thaisce a ghlanadh agus do bhrabhsálaí a atosú freisin."

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/)
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:193
msgid "The Library Bundle is a collection of resources for which no application is required. If you meet the criteria laid out above, you will be authorized for access automatically upon logging in to the platform. Only some of our content is currently included in the Library Bundle, however we hope to expand the collection as more publishers become comfortable with participating. All Bundle content is accessed via EZProxy."
msgstr "Is bailiúchán acmhainní é an Pacáiste Leabharlainne nach bhfuil aon iarratas ag teastáil ina leith. Má chomhlíonann tú na critéir atá leagtha amach thuas, údarófar rochtain duit go huathoibríoch nuair a logálann tú isteach san ardán. Níl ach cuid dár n-ábhar san áireamh sa Phacáiste Leabharlainne faoi láthair, ach tá súil againn an bailiúchán a leathnú de réir mar a bhíonn níos mó foilsitheoirí compordach le bheith rannpháirteach. Is féidir rochtain a fháil ar gach ábhar sa Phacáiste trí EZProxy."

#. Translators: This is the heading for a section on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:202
msgid "Citation practices"
msgstr "Cleachtais lua"

#. Translators: This text is found on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#: TWLight/templates/about.html:206
msgid "Citation practices vary by project and even by article. Generally, we support editors citing where they found information, in a form that allows others to check it for themselves. That often means providing both original source details as well as a link to the partner database in which the source was found."
msgstr "Athraíonn cleachtais lua de réir tionscadail agus fiú de réir alt. Go ginearálta, tacaímid le heagarthóirí a luann cá bhfuair siad faisnéis, i bhfoirm a ligeann do dhaoine eile í a sheiceáil dóibh féin. Is minic a chiallaíonn sé sin sonraí faoin bhfoinse bhunaidh a sholáthar chomh maith le nasc chuig bunachar sonraí an chomhpháirtíochta inar aimsíodh an fhoinse."

#. Translators: This is the heading for a section on the About page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/about/).
#. Translators: This link is at the bottom of every page and can be clicked by users to contact the wikipedia library team.
