#. Translators: This is the title of the page where users can request we stop processing their data.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/restrict_data.html:11
msgid "Restrict data processing"
msgstr "Srian a chur le próiseáil sonraí"

#. Translators: This message is displayed on the page where users can request we stop processing their data.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/restrict_data.html:15
msgid "Checking this box and clicking “Restrict” will pause all processing of the data you have entered into this website. You will not be able to apply for access to resources, your applications will not be further processed, and none of your data will be altered, until you return to this page and uncheck the box. This is not the same as deleting your data."
msgstr "Má sheiceálann tú an bosca seo agus má chliceálann tú ar “Srian”, cuirfear sos ar phróiseáil na sonraí atá curtha isteach agat ar an suíomh Gréasáin seo. Ní bheidh tú in ann iarratas a dhéanamh ar rochtain ar acmhainní, ní dhéanfar tuilleadh próiseála ar d’iarratais, agus ní athrófar aon cheann de do shonraí, go dtí go bhfillfidh tú ar an leathanach seo agus go mbainfidh tú an tic den bhosca. Ní hionann é seo agus do shonraí a scriosadh."

#. Translators: This warning message is shown to coordinators who view the data restriction page.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/restrict_data.html:26
msgid "You are a coordinator on this site. If you restrict the processing of your data, your coordinator flag will be removed."
msgstr "Is comhordaitheoir thú ar an suíomh seo. Má chuireann tú srian le próiseáil do shonraí, bainfear bratach do chomhordaitheora."

#. Translators: use the date *when you are translating*, in a language-appropriate format.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:33
msgid "Last updated 11 August 2021"
msgstr "Nuashonraithe go deireanach 11 Lúnasa 2021"

#. Translators: This link is on the Terms of Use page and links to the Wikimedia Foundation Privacy Policy (https://wikimediafoundation.org/wiki/Privacy_policy). Wikimedia Foundation should not be translated.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:37
msgid "Wikimedia Foundation privacy policy"
msgstr "Polasaí príobháideachta Fhondúireacht Wikimedia"

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:41
msgid "Wikipedia Library Card Terms of Use and Privacy Statement"
msgstr "Téarmaí Úsáide agus Ráiteas Príobháideachais Cárta Leabharlainne Vicipéid"

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:51
msgid "<a class=\"twl-links\" href=\"https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library\"> The Wikipedia Library </a> has partnered with publishers around the world to allow users to access otherwise paywalled resources. This website allows Wikipedia editors to search and access these resources."
msgstr "Tá comhpháirtíocht déanta ag <a class=\"twl-links\" href=\"https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library\">Leabharlann Vicipéide</a> le foilsitheoirí ar fud an domhain chun ligean d'úsáideoirí rochtain a fháil ar acmhainní a mbeadh ballaí íoctha leo murach sin. Ligeann an suíomh Gréasáin seo d'eagarthóirí Vicipéide na hacmhainní seo a chuardach agus rochtain a fháil orthu."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Wikimedia Foundation should not be translated. WMF should not be translated. Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:63
msgid "This program is administered by the Wikimedia Foundation (WMF). These terms of use and privacy notice pertain to your application for access to resources through the Wikipedia Library, your use of this website, and your access to and use of those resources. They also describe our handling of the information you provide to us in order to create and administer your Wikipedia Library account. If we make material changes to the terms, we will notify users."
msgstr "Tá an clár seo á riaradh ag Fondúireacht Wikimedia (WMF). Baineann na téarmaí úsáide agus an fógra príobháideachais seo le d’iarratas ar rochtain ar acmhainní trí Leabharlann Vicipéid, d’úsáid den suíomh Gréasáin seo, agus do rochtain ar na hacmhainní sin agus d’úsáid astu. Déanann siad cur síos freisin ar an gcaoi a láimhseálann muid an fhaisnéis a sholáthraíonn tú dúinn chun do chuntas Leabharlann Vicipéid a chruthú agus a riaradh. Má dhéanaimid athruithe ábhartha ar na téarmaí, cuirfimid úsáideoirí ar an eolas."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:74
msgid "Requirements for a Wikipedia Library Card Account"
msgstr "Riachtanais le haghaidh Cuntas Cárta Leabharlainne Vicipéid"

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:78
msgid "Access to resources via The Wikipedia Library is reserved for community members who have demonstrated their commitment to the Wikimedia projects, and who will use their access to these resources to improve project content. To that end, in order to be eligible for The Wikipedia Library, we require that you be registered for a user account on the projects, with at least 500 edits, six (6) months of activity, and 10+ edits in the last month. We ask that you do not request access to any publishers with a limited number of available accounts whose resources you can already access for free through your local library or university, or another institution or organization, in order to provide that opportunity to others."
msgstr "Tá rochtain ar acmhainní trí Leabharlann Vicipéid curtha in áirithe do bhaill den phobal a léirigh a dtiomantas do thionscadail Wikimedia, agus a úsáidfidh a rochtain ar na hacmhainní seo chun ábhar an tionscadail a fheabhsú. Chuige sin, chun a bheith incháilithe do Leabharlann Vicipéid, ní mór duit cuntas úsáideora a chlárú ar na tionscadail, le 500 eagarthóireacht ar a laghad, sé (6) mhí gníomhaíochta, agus 10+ eagarthóireacht le mí anuas. Iarraimid ort gan rochtain a iarraidh ar aon fhoilsitheoirí a bhfuil líon teoranta cuntas ar fáil acu ar féidir leat rochtain a fháil ar a gcuid acmhainní cheana féin saor in aisce trí do leabharlann áitiúil nó ollscoil, nó institiúid nó eagraíocht eile, chun an deis sin a thabhairt do dhaoine eile."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:94
msgid "Additionally, if you are currently blocked or banned from a Wikimedia project, applications to resources may be rejected or restricted. If you obtain a Wikipedia Library account, but a block or ban is subsequently instituted against you on one of the projects, you may lose access to your Wikipedia Library account."
msgstr "Ina theannta sin, má tá tú blocáilte nó toirmiscthe faoi láthair ó thionscadal Wikimedia, féadfar iarratais ar acmhainní a dhiúltú nó a shrianadh. Má fhaigheann tú cuntas Leabharlann Vicipéid, ach má chuirtear bac nó cosc ​​​​i do choinne ina dhiaidh sin ar cheann de na tionscadail, féadfaidh tú rochtain ar do chuntas Leabharlann Vicipéid a chailleadh."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:104
msgid "Your eligibility to access The Wikipedia Library is assessed at each login. While more than half of the library's content is provided via this automated eligibility check, access to other publisher's content may be time limited, typically lapsing after one year, after which you will usually need to apply for renewal."
msgstr "Déantar measúnú ar d’incháilitheacht chun rochtain a fháil ar Leabharlann Vicipéid ag gach logáil isteach. Cé go soláthraítear níos mó ná leath d’ábhar na leabharlainne tríd an tseiceáil incháilitheachta uathoibrithe seo, d’fhéadfadh rochtain ar ábhar foilsitheoirí eile a bheith teoranta ó thaobh ama de, agus de ghnáth rachaidh sé in éag tar éis bliana amháin, agus ina dhiaidh sin beidh ort iarratas a dhéanamh ar athnuachan de ghnáth."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:114
msgid "Applying via Your Wikipedia Library Card Account"
msgstr "Ag cur isteach trí do chuntas cárta leabharlainne Vicipéide"

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:118
msgid "In order to apply for access to a partner resource, you must provide us with certain information, which we will use to evaluate your application. If your application is approved, we may transfer the information you have given us to the publishers whose resources you wish to access. They will either contact you with the account information directly or we will send access information to you ourselves."
msgstr "Chun iarratas a dhéanamh ar rochtain ar acmhainn chomhpháirtíochta, ní mór duit faisnéis áirithe a sholáthar dúinn, a úsáidfimid chun d’iarratas a mheas. Má cheadaítear d’iarratas, féadfaimid an fhaisnéis atá tugtha agat dúinn a aistriú chuig na foilsitheoirí ar mian leat rochtain a fháil ar a gcuid acmhainní. Déanfaidh siad teagmháil leat go díreach leis an bhfaisnéis chuntais nó seolfaimid faisnéis rochtana chugat féin."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:130
msgid "In addition to the basic information you provide to us, our system will retrieve some information directly from the Wikimedia projects: your username, email address, edit count, registration date, user ID number, groups to which you belong, and any special user rights."
msgstr "Chomh maith leis an bhfaisnéis bhunúsach a sholáthraíonn tú dúinn, gheobhaidh ár gcóras roinnt faisnéise go díreach ó thionscadail Wikimedia: d'ainm úsáideora, do sheoladh ríomhphoist, líon na n-eagarthóireacht, dáta clárúcháin, uimhir aitheantais úsáideora, grúpaí lena mbaineann tú, agus aon chearta speisialta úsáideora."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:140
msgid "Each time you log in to the Wikipedia Library Card Platform, this information will be automatically updated."
msgstr "Gach uair a logálann tú isteach ar Ardán Cárta Leabharlainne Vicipéid, déanfar an fhaisnéis seo a nuashonrú go huathoibríoch."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:148
msgid "We will ask you to provide us with some information about your history of contributions to the Wikimedia projects. Information on contribution history is optional, but will greatly assist us in evaluating your application."
msgstr "Iarrfaimid ort roinnt eolais a thabhairt dúinn faoi stair do ranníocaíochtaí le tionscadail Wikimedia. Is rogha é eolas faoi stair na ranníocaíochtaí, ach cabhróidh sé go mór linn d’iarratas a mheas."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). WMF should not be translated. Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:157
msgid "The information you provide when creating your account will be visible to you while on the site but not to others unless they are approved Wikipedia Library Coordinators, WMF Staff, or WMF Contractors who need access to this data in order to carry out their work with the Wikipedia Library, all of whom are subject to non-disclosure obligations."
msgstr "Beidh an fhaisnéis a sholáthraíonn tú agus do chuntas á chruthú agat le feiceáil agat agus tú ar an suíomh ach ní bheidh sí le feiceáil ag daoine eile mura Comhordaitheoirí Leabharlainne Vicipéide ceadaithe, Foireann WMF, nó Conraitheoirí WMF iad a bhfuil rochtain acu ar na sonraí seo chun a gcuid oibre a dhéanamh le Leabharlann Vicipéide, agus tá oibleagáidí rúndachta ag gabháil leo uile."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:167
msgid "Your Use of Publisher Resources"
msgstr "D'Úsáid Acmhainní Foilsitheora"

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:171
msgid "In order to access an individual publisher’s resources, you must agree to that publisher’s terms of use and privacy policy. You agree that you will not violate such terms and policies in connection with your use of the Wikipedia Library. Additionally, the following activities are prohibited while accessing publisher resources through the Wikipedia Library."
msgstr "Chun rochtain a fháil ar acmhainní foilsitheora aonair, ní mór duit aontú le téarmaí úsáide agus polasaí príobháideachta an fhoilsitheora sin. Aontaíonn tú nach sáróidh tú na téarmaí agus na beartais sin i ndáil le d’úsáid de Leabharlann Vicipéid. Ina theannta sin, tá na gníomhaíochtaí seo a leanas toirmiscthe agus rochtain á fáil agat ar acmhainní foilsitheora trí Leabharlann Vicipéid."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:184
msgid "Sharing your Wikipedia account, usernames, passwords, or any access codes for publisher resources with others;"
msgstr "Do chuntas Vicipéide, ainmneacha úsáideora, pasfhocail nó aon chóid rochtana le haghaidh acmhainní foilsitheora a roinnt le daoine eile;"

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:191
msgid "Automatically scraping or downloading restricted content from publishers;"
msgstr "Ábhar srianta a scríobadh nó a íoslódáil go huathoibríoch ó fhoilsitheoirí;"

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:197
msgid "Systematically making printed or electronic copies of multiple extracts of restricted content available for any purpose;"
msgstr "Cóipeanna clóite nó leictreonacha de shleachta iolracha d’ábhar srianta a chur ar fáil go córasach chun aon chríche;"

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:204
msgid "Data mining metadata without permission—for example, in order to use metadata for auto-created stub articles;"
msgstr "Meiteashonraí mianadóireachta sonraí gan chead—mar shampla, chun meiteashonraí a úsáid le haghaidh ailt stumpa a chruthaítear go huathoibríoch;"

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:211
msgid "Using the access you receive through the Wikipedia Library for profit by selling access to your account or resources which you have through it."
msgstr "An rochtain a fhaigheann tú tríd an Leabharlann Vicipéid a úsáid chun brabús a dhéanamh trí rochtain ar do chuntas nó ar acmhainní atá agat tríd an leabharlann a dhíol."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:220
msgid "External Search and Proxy Services"
msgstr "Seirbhísí Cuardaigh agus Seachfhreastalaí Seachtracha"

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:224
msgid "Certain resources may only be accessed using an external search service, such as the EBSCO Discovery Service, or a proxy service, such as OCLC EZProxy. If you use such external search and/or proxy services, please review the applicable terms of use and privacy policies."
msgstr "Ní féidir rochtain a fháil ar acmhainní áirithe ach amháin trí sheirbhís chuardaigh sheachtrach, amhail Seirbhís Fionnachtana EBSCO, nó seirbhís seachfhreastalaí, amhail OCLC EZProxy. Má úsáideann tú seirbhísí cuardaigh agus/nó seachfhreastalaí seachtracha den sórt sin, léigh na téarmaí úsáide agus na beartais phríobháideachais is infheidhme."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:234
msgid "In addition, if you use OCLC EZProxy, please note that you may not use it for commercial purposes."
msgstr "Ina theannta sin, má úsáideann tú OCLC EZProxy, tabhair faoi deara nach féidir leat é a úsáid chun críocha tráchtála."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:241
msgid "Data Retention and Handling"
msgstr "Coinneáil agus Láimhseáil Sonraí"

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Wikimedia Foundation should not be translated. Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:245
msgid "The Wikimedia Foundation and our service providers use your information for the legitimate purpose of providing Wikipedia Library services in support of our charitable mission. When you apply for a Wikipedia Library account, or use your Wikipedia Library account, we may routinely collect the following information: your username, email address, edit count, registration date, user ID number, groups to which you belong, and any special user rights; your name, country of residence, and/or affiliation, if required by a partner to which you are applying; your narrative description of your contributions and reasons for applying for access to partner resources; and the date you agree to these terms of use."
msgstr "Úsáideann Fondúireacht Wikimedia agus ár soláthraithe seirbhíse d’fhaisnéis chun críche dlisteanaí seirbhísí Leabharlann Vicipéid a sholáthar chun tacú lenár misean carthanachta. Nuair a dhéanann tú iarratas ar chuntas Leabharlann Vicipéid, nó nuair a úsáideann tú do chuntas Leabharlann Vicipéid, féadfaimid an fhaisnéis seo a leanas a bhailiú go rialta: d’ainm úsáideora, do sheoladh ríomhphoist, líon na n-eagarthóireacht, dáta clárúcháin, uimhir aitheantais úsáideora, grúpaí lena mbaineann tú, agus aon chearta speisialta úsáideora; d’ainm, do thír chónaithe, agus/nó do chleamhnas, más gá don chomhpháirtí a bhfuil tú ag déanamh iarratais air; do chur síos insinte ar do chuid ranníocaíochtaí agus na cúiseanna le hiarratas a dhéanamh ar rochtain ar acmhainní comhpháirtíochta; agus an dáta a n-aontaíonn tú leis na téarmaí úsáide seo."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:262
#, python-format
msgid "Each publisher who is a member of the Wikipedia Library program requires different specific information in the application. Some publishers may request only an email address, while others request more detailed data, such as your name, location, or institutional affiliation. When you complete your application, you will only be asked to supply information required by the publishers you have chosen, and each publisher will only receive the information they require for providing you with access. Please see our <a class=\"twl-links\" href=\"%(all_partners_url)s\">partner information</a> pages to learn what information is required by each publisher to gain access to their resources."
msgstr "Éilíonn gach foilsitheoir atá ina bhall de chlár Leabharlann Vicipéid faisnéis shonrach dhifriúil san iarratas. D’fhéadfadh roinnt foilsitheoirí seoladh ríomhphoist amháin a iarraidh, agus d’fhéadfadh daoine eile sonraí níos mionsonraithe a iarraidh, amhail d’ainm, do shuíomh, nó do chleamhnas institiúideach. Nuair a chomhlánaíonn tú d’iarratas, ní iarrfar ort ach an fhaisnéis a theastaíonn ó na foilsitheoirí a roghnaigh tú a sholáthar, agus ní bhfaighidh gach foilsitheoir ach an fhaisnéis a theastaíonn uathu chun rochtain a thabhairt duit. Féach ar ár leathanaigh <a class=\"twl-links\" href=\"%(all_partners_url)s\">eolas comhpháirtíochta</a> le foghlaim cén fhaisnéis a theastaíonn ó gach foilsitheoir chun rochtain a fháil ar a n-acmhainní."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Wikimedia Foundation should not be translated. Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:277
msgid "Some Wikipedia Library pages are visible without logging in, but you will need to log in to apply or access proprietary partner resources. We use the data provided by you via OAuth and Wikimedia API calls to assess your application for access and to process approved requests."
msgstr "Tá roinnt leathanaigh Leabharlann Vicipéid le feiceáil gan logáil isteach, ach beidh ort logáil isteach chun iarratas a dhéanamh nó rochtain a fháil ar acmhainní comhpháirtíochta dílseánaigh. Úsáidimid na sonraí a sholáthraíonn tú trí ghlaonna OAuth agus Wikimedia API chun d’iarratas ar rochtain a mheas agus chun iarratais cheadaithe a phróiseáil."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:288
#, python-format
msgid "In order to administer the Wikipedia Library program, we will retain the application data we collect from you for three years after your most recent login, unless you delete your account, as described below. You can log in and go to <a class=\"twl-links\" href=\"%(profile_url)s\">your profile page</a> in order to see the information associated with your account, and can download it in JSON format. You may access, update, restrict, or delete this information at any time, except for the information that is automatically retrieved from the projects. If you have any questions or concerns about the handling of your data, please contact <a class=\"twl-links\" href=\"mailto:wikipedialibrary@wikimedia.org?Subject=Wikipedia%%20Library%%20Card%%20account%%20deactivation\"> wikipedialibrary@wikimedia.org </a>."
msgstr "Chun clár Leabharlann Vicipéid a riaradh, coimeádfaimid na sonraí feidhmchláir a bhailímid uait ar feadh trí bliana tar éis do logáil isteach is déanaí, mura scriosann tú do chuntas, mar a thuairiscítear thíos. Is féidir leat logáil isteach agus dul chuig <a class=\"twl-links\" href=\"%(profile_url)s\">do leathanach próifíle</a> chun an fhaisnéis a bhaineann le do chuntas a fheiceáil, agus is féidir leat é a íoslódáil i bhformáid JSON. Féadfaidh tú rochtain a fháil ar an bhfaisnéis seo, í a nuashonrú, a shrianadh nó a scriosadh ag am ar bith, seachas an fhaisnéis a aisghabhtar go huathoibríoch ó na tionscadail. Má tá aon cheist nó imní ort faoi láimhseáil do shonraí, déan teagmháil le <a class=\"twl-links\" href=\"mailto:wikipedialibrary@wikimedia.org?Subject=Wikipedia%%20Library%%20Card%%20account%%20deactivation\"> wikipedialibrary@wikimedia.org </a>."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:305
msgid "If you decide to disable your Wikipedia Library account, you can use the delete button on your profile to delete certain personal information associated with your account. We will delete your real name, institutional affiliation, and country of residence. Please note that the system will retain a record of your username, the publishers to which you applied or had access, and the dates of that access. Note that deletion is not reversible. Deletion of your Wikipedia Library account may also correspond with the removal of any resource access to which you were eligible or approved. If you request the deletion of account information and later wish to apply for a new account, you will need to provide the necessary information again."
msgstr "Má shocraíonn tú do chuntas Leabharlann Vicipéide a dhíchumasú, is féidir leat an cnaipe scriosta ar do phróifíl a úsáid chun faisnéis phearsanta áirithe a bhaineann le do chuntas a scriosadh. Scriosfaimid d’ainm fíor, do chleamhnas institiúideach, agus do thír chónaithe. Tabhair faoi deara, le do thoil, go gcoimeádfaidh an córas taifead de d’ainm úsáideora, na foilsitheoirí ar chuir tú isteach orthu nó ar raibh rochtain agat orthu, agus dátaí na rochtana sin. Tabhair faoi deara nach féidir an scriosadh a aisiompú. Féadfaidh scriosadh do chuntais Leabharlann Vicipéide a bheith comhfhreagrach le baint aon rochtana acmhainní a raibh tú incháilithe dóibh nó a raibh cead agat dóibh. Má iarrann tú faisnéis chuntais a scriosadh agus más mian leat iarratas a dhéanamh ar chuntas nua níos déanaí, beidh ort an fhaisnéis riachtanach a sholáthar arís."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). WMF should not be translated. Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:321
msgid "The Wikipedia Library is run by WMF Staff, Contractors, and approved volunteer Coordinators. The data associated with your account will be shared with the WMF staff, contractors, service providers, and volunteer coordinators who need to process the information in connection with their work for the Wikipedia Library, and who are subject to confidentiality obligations. We will also use your data for internal Wikipedia Library purposes such as distributing user surveys and account notifications, and in a depersonalized or aggregated fashion for statistical analysis and administration. Finally, we will share your information with the publishers whom you specifically select in order to provide you with access to resources. Otherwise, your information will not be shared with third parties, with the exception of the circumstances described below."
msgstr "Tá Leabharlann Vicipéid á reáchtáil ag Foireann, Conraitheoirí, agus Comhordaitheoirí deonacha ceadaithe WMF. Roinnfear na sonraí a bhaineann le do chuntas le foireann, conraitheoirí, soláthraithe seirbhíse, agus comhordaitheoirí deonacha WMF a gcaithfidh an fhaisnéis a phróiseáil i ndáil lena gcuid oibre do Leabharlann Vicipéid, agus atá faoi réir oibleagáidí rúndachta. Úsáidfimid do shonraí freisin chun críocha inmheánacha Leabharlann Vicipéid amhail suirbhéanna úsáideoirí agus fógraí cuntais a dháileadh, agus ar bhealach díphearsantaithe nó comhiomlánaithe le haghaidh anailíse agus riaracháin staitistiúla. Ar deireadh, roinnfimid d’fhaisnéis leis na foilsitheoirí a roghnaíonn tú go sonrach chun rochtain ar acmhainní a sholáthar duit. Seachas sin, ní roinnfear d’fhaisnéis le tríú páirtithe, seachas sna himthosca a thuairiscítear thíos."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). WMF should not be translated.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:338
msgid "We may disclose any collected information when required by law, when we have your permission, when needed to protect our rights, privacy, safety, users, or the general public, and when necessary to enforce these terms, WMF’s general <a class=\"twl-links\" href=\"https://foundation.wikimedia.org/wiki/Terms_of_Use\">Terms of Use</a>, or any other WMF policy."
msgstr "Féadfaimid aon fhaisnéis bhailithe a nochtadh nuair a cheanglaítear orainn de réir dlí, nuair a bheidh do chead againn, nuair is gá chun ár gcearta, ár bpríobháideacht, ár sábháilteacht, úsáideoirí, nó an pobal i gcoitinne a chosaint, agus nuair is gá chun na téarmaí seo, Téarmaí Úsáide ginearálta WMF, nó aon pholasaí eile de chuid WMF a fhorfheidhmiú."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:349
msgid "We take the security of your personal data seriously, and take reasonable precautions to ensure your data is protected. These precautions include access controls to limit who has access to your data and security technologies to protect data stored on the server. However, we cannot guarantee the safety of your data as it is transmitted and stored."
msgstr "Glacaimid slándáil do shonraí pearsanta dáiríre, agus glacaimid réamhchúraimí réasúnta chun a chinntiú go bhfuil do shonraí cosanta. Áirítear leis na réamhchúraimí seo rialuithe rochtana chun teorainn a chur le cé a bhfuil rochtain aige ar do shonraí agus teicneolaíochtaí slándála chun sonraí atá stóráilte ar an bhfreastalaí a chosaint. Mar sin féin, ní féidir linn sábháilteacht do shonraí a ráthú agus iad á dtarchur agus á stóráil."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:360
msgid "Please note that these terms do not control the use and handling of your data by the publishers and service providers whose resources you access or apply to access. Please read their individual privacy policies for that information."
msgstr "Tabhair faoi deara nach rialaíonn na téarmaí seo úsáid agus láimhseáil do shonraí ag na foilsitheoirí agus na soláthraithe seirbhíse a bhfuil rochtain agat ar a gcuid acmhainní nó a ndéanann tú iarratas chun rochtain a fháil orthu. Léigh a mbeartais phríobháideachais aonair le haghaidh na faisnéise sin."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:368
msgid "Important Note"
msgstr "Nóta Tábhachtach"

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Wikimedia Foundation should not be translated. Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:373
msgid "The Wikimedia Foundation is a nonprofit organization based in San Francisco, California. The Wikipedia Library program provides access to resources held by publishers in multiple countries. If you apply for a Wikipedia Library account (whether you are inside or outside of the United States), you understand that your personal data will be collected, transferred, stored, processed, disclosed and otherwise used in the U.S. as described in this privacy policy. You also understand that your information may be transferred by us from the U.S. to other countries, which may have different or less stringent data protection laws than your country, in connection with providing services to you, including evaluating your application and securing access to your chosen publishers (locations for each publisher are outlined on their respective partner information pages)."
msgstr "Is eagraíocht neamhbhrabúis í Fondúireacht Wikimedia atá lonnaithe i San Francisco, California. Soláthraíonn clár Leabharlann Vicipéid rochtain ar acmhainní atá i seilbh foilsitheoirí i dtíortha éagsúla. Má dhéanann tú iarratas ar chuntas Leabharlann Vicipéid (cibé acu atá tú laistigh nó lasmuigh de na Stáit Aontaithe), tuigeann tú go ndéanfar do shonraí pearsanta a bhailiú, a aistriú, a stóráil, a phróiseáil, a nochtadh agus a úsáid ar shlí eile sna Stáit Aontaithe mar a thuairiscítear sa pholasaí príobháideachais seo. Tuigeann tú freisin go bhféadfaimid d’fhaisnéis a aistriú ó na Stáit Aontaithe go tíortha eile, a bhféadfadh dlíthe cosanta sonraí difriúla nó níos lú déine a bheith acu ná do thír féin, i ndáil le seirbhísí a sholáthar duit, lena n-áirítear d’iarratas a mheas agus rochtain a fháil ar na foilsitheoirí a roghnaigh tú (tá suíomhanna gach foilsitheora leagtha amach ar a leathanaigh faisnéise comhpháirtíochta faoi seach)."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:392
msgid "Please note that in the event of any differences in meaning or interpretation between the original English version of these terms and a translation, the original English version takes precedence."
msgstr "Tabhair faoi deara, le do thoil, i gcás aon difríochtaí i gciall nó i léirmhíniú idir an leagan Béarla bunaidh de na téarmaí seo agus aistriúchán, go mbeidh tosaíocht ag an leagan Béarla bunaidh."

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Wikimedia Foundation should not be translated.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:403
msgid "See also the <a class=\"twl-links\" href=\"https://wikimediafoundation.org/wiki/Privacy_policy\">Wikimedia Foundation Privacy Policy</a>."
msgstr "Féach freisin ar <a class=\"twl-links\" href=\"https://wikimediafoundation.org/wiki/Privacy_policy\">Polasaí Príobháideachais Fhondúireacht Wikimedia</a>."

#. Translators: This is the second to last line of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/).
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:412
msgid "Thank you!"
msgstr "Go raibh maith agat!"

#. Translators: This is the last line of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:416
msgid "The Wikipedia Library Team"
msgstr "Foireann Leabharlann Vicipéid"

#. Translators: This is the last line of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Wikimedia Foundation should not be translated.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:418
msgid "Wikimedia Foundation"
msgstr "Fondúireacht Wikimedia"

#. Translators: This is a section of the Terms of Use (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/terms/). Translate Wikipedia Library in the same way as the global branch is named in the language you are translating (click through the language from https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/The_Wikipedia_Library/Global). If the language is not available, do not translate Wikipedia Library.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/terms.html:426
msgid "By checking this box and clicking “Submit”, you agree that you have read the above terms and that you will adhere to the terms of use in your application to and use of the The Wikipedia Library, and the publishers’ services to which you gain access through The Wikipedia Library program."
msgstr "Tríd an mbosca seo a sheiceáil agus cliceáil ar “Cuir Isteach”, aontaíonn tú gur léigh tú na téarmaí thuas agus go gcloífidh tú leis na téarmaí úsáide i d’iarratas ar Leabharlann Vicipéid agus in úsáid na Leabharlann Vicipéide, agus seirbhísí na bhfoilsitheoirí a bhfaigheann tú rochtain orthu trí chlár Leabharlann Vicipéide."

#: TWLight/users/templates/users/user_collection_tile.html:32
msgid "Remove this collection from favorites"
msgstr "Bain an bailiúchán seo ó na cinn is fearr leat"

#: TWLight/users/templates/users/user_collection_tile.html:38
msgid "Add this collection to favorites"
msgstr "Cuir an bailiúchán seo le is fearr leat"

#. Translators: On the My Library page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/users/my_library), this labels when a subscription on a collection expired.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/user_collection_tile.html:102
msgid "Expiry date"
msgstr "Dáta éaga"

#: TWLight/users/templates/users/user_collection_tile.html:107
msgid "Click to return this access"
msgstr "Cliceáil chun an rochtain seo a thabhairt ar ais"

#. Translators: On the My Library page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/users/my_library), this labels the text on a button which takes the user to an open application.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/user_collection_tile.html:117
msgid "Go to application"
msgstr "Téigh chuig an iarratas"

#. Translators: On the My Library page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/users/my_library), this labels the text on a button which takes the user to the partner's site.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/user_collection_tile.html:131
msgid "Go to site"
msgstr "Téigh go dtí an suíomh"

#. Translators: On the My Library page (https://wikipedialibrary.wmflabs.org/users/my_library), this labels the text on a button which takes the user to the partner's site.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/user_collection_tile.html:134
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/user_collection_tile.html:161
msgid "Access collection"
msgstr "Rochtain ar bhailiúchán"

#. Translators: Labels a button users can click to renew an expired account.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/user_collection_tile.html:146
msgid "Renew"
msgstr "Athnuachan"

#. Translators: Labels a button users can click to extend the duration of their access.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/user_collection_tile.html:149
msgid "Extend"
msgstr "Leathnaigh"

#. Translators: This is the heading of the page where users can request the deletion of their data.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/user_confirm_delete.html:11
msgid "Delete all data"
msgstr "Scrios na sonraí go léir"

#. Translators: This message is displayed on the page where users can request the deletion of their data.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/user_confirm_delete.html:17
msgid "<b>Warning:</b> Performing this action will delete your Wikipedia Library Card user account and all associated applications. This process is not reversible. You may lose any partner accounts you were granted, and will not be able to renew those accounts or apply for new ones."
msgstr "<b>Rabhadh:</b> Scriosfar do chuntas úsáideora Cárta Leabharlainne Vicipéide agus na feidhmchláir ghaolmhara go léir má dhéantar an gníomh seo. Ní féidir an próiseas seo a aisiompú. Féadfaidh tú aon chuntais chomhpháirtíochta a deonaíodh duit a chailleadh, agus ní bheidh tú in ann na cuntais sin a athnuachan ná iarratas a dhéanamh ar chinn nua."

#. Translators: this should show up for people who log in with a username/password and not OAuth, so we don't know what their Wikipedia identity is.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/user_detail.html:12
#, python-format
msgid "Hi, %(username)s! You don't have a Wikipedia editor profile attached to your account here, so you are probably a site administrator."
msgstr "Haigh, %(username)s! Níl próifíl eagarthóra Vicipéide ceangailte le do chuntas anseo, mar sin is dócha gur riarthóir suímh thú."

#. Translators: In the unlikely scenario that someone is able to register an account without using OAuth (thus leaving us without some of the information required for applications), users will see this message, encouraging them to re-register.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/user_detail.html:20
msgid "If you aren't a site administrator, something weird has happened. You won't be able to apply for access without a Wikipedia editor profile. You should log out and create a new account by logging in via OAuth, or contact a site administrator for help."
msgstr "Mura riarthóir suímh thú, tá rud éigin aisteach tarlaithe. Ní bheidh tú in ann iarratas a dhéanamh ar rochtain gan phróifíl eagarthóra Vicipéide. Ba chóir duit logáil amach agus cuntas nua a chruthú trí logáil isteach trí OAuth, nó teagmháil a dhéanamh le riarthóir suímh le haghaidh cabhrach."

#. Translators: Labels a sections where coordinators can select their email preferences.
#: TWLight/users/templates/users/user_email_preferences.html:15
msgid "Coordinators only"
msgstr "Comhordaitheoirí amháin"

#. Translators: This message is shown on user's own profile page, encouraging them to make sure their information is up to date, so that account coordinators can use the information to judge applications.
#: TWLight/users/views.py:180
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Please <a class='twl-links' href='{url}'>update your contributions</a> to Wikipedia to help coordinators evaluate your applications."
msgstr "Please <a class='twl-links' href='{url}'>update your contributions</a> to Wikipedia to help coordinators evaluate your applications."

#. Translators: Coordinators are shown this message when they unselect all three types of reminder email options under preferences.
#: TWLight/users/views.py:292
msgid "You have chosen not to receive reminder emails. As a coordinator, you should receive at least one type of reminder emails, so consider changing your preferences."
msgstr "Tá tú tar éis a roghnú gan ríomhphoist meabhrúcháin a fháil. Mar chomhordaitheoir, ba cheart duit cineál amháin ríomhphoist meabhrúcháin ar a laghad a fháil, mar sin smaoinigh ar do chuid roghanna a athrú."

#. Translators: Coordinators are shown this message when they make changes to their reminder email options under preferences.
#: TWLight/users/views.py:300
msgid "Your reminder email preferences are updated."
msgstr "Tá do chuid roghanna ríomhphoist meabhrúcháin nuashonraithe."

#. Translators: This message is shown to users who attempt to update their personal information without being logged in.
#. Translators: If a user tries to do something (such as updating their email) when not logged in, this message is presented.
#. Translators: This message is shown to users who attempt to update their data processing without being logged in.
#: TWLight/users/views.py:382 TWLight/users/views.py:468
#: TWLight/users/views.py:521
msgid "You must be logged in to do that."
msgstr "Ní mór duit a bheith logáilte isteach chun é sin a dhéanamh."

#. Translators: Shown to the user when they successfully modify their personal information.
#: TWLight/users/views.py:415
msgid "Your information has been updated."
msgstr "Tá d’fhaisnéis nuashonraithe."

#. Translators: If a user tries to save the 'email change form' without entering one and checking the 'use my Wikipedia email address' checkbox, this message is presented.
#: TWLight/users/views.py:452
msgid "Both the values cannot be blank. Either enter a email or check the box."
msgstr "Ní féidir an dá luach a fhágáil bán. Cuir isteach ríomhphost nó cuir tic sa bhosca."

#. Translators: Shown to users when they successfully modify their email. Don't translate {email}.
#: TWLight/users/views.py:480
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Your email has been changed to {email}."
msgstr "Tá do sheoladh ríomhphoist athraithe go {email}."

#. Translators: If the user has not filled out their email, they can browse the website but cannot apply for access to resources.
#: TWLight/users/views.py:491
msgid "Your email is blank. You can still explore the site, but you won't be able to apply for access to partner resources without an email."
msgstr "Tá do ríomhphost bán. Is féidir leat an suíomh a iniúchadh fós, ach ní bheidh tú in ann iarratas a dhéanamh ar rochtain ar acmhainní comhpháirtíochta gan ríomhphost."

#. Translators: This message is shown once the access to a partner has successfully been returned.
#: TWLight/users/views.py:805
msgid "Access to {} has been returned."
msgstr "Tá rochtain ar {} tugtha ar ais."

#. Translators: This text is shown next to a tick or cross denoting whether the current user has made more than 500 edits from their Wikimedia account.
#: TWLight/users/views.py:884 TWLight/views.py:43
msgid "500+ edits"
msgstr "500+ eagarthóireacht"

#. Translators: This text is shown next to a tick or cross denoting whether the current user has Wikimedia account that is at least 6 months old.
#: TWLight/users/views.py:886 TWLight/views.py:45
msgid "6+ months editing"
msgstr "6+ mí d'eagarthóireacht"

#. Translators: This text is shown next to a tick or cross denoting whether the current user has made more than 10 edits within the last month (30 days) from their Wikimedia account.
#: TWLight/users/views.py:888
msgid "10+ edits in the last month"
msgstr "10+ eagarthóireacht le mí anuas"

#. Translators: This text is shown next to a tick or cross denoting whether the current user's Wikimedia account has been blocked on any project.
#: TWLight/users/views.py:890 TWLight/views.py:49
msgid "No active blocks"
msgstr "Gan aon bhloic ghníomhacha"

#. Translators: This text is shown next to a tick or cross denoting whether the current user has made more than 10 edits within the last 30 days from their Wikimedia account.
#: TWLight/views.py:47
msgid "10+ edits in the last 30 days"
msgstr "10+ eagarthóireacht le 30 lá anuas"

